value.title: StarCraft 2: NEW PATCH IS LIVE - Zerg vs Protoss is GOOD?! (herO vs Rogue)

The new patch primarily addresses this ZvP matchup, nerfing Shield Batteries, Dark Templar, Queens, Lurkers, Void Rays and buffing the Nydus Worm slightly.
